PM Indiya don halartar gawurtaccen haikali a wurin da aka yi jayayya
Sabon Delhi (AP) - Firayi Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci wani kasaitaccen bikin da za a yi a watan gobe na haikalin Hindu a wani wurin da ake jayayya a arewacin Indiya inda aka rushe wani masallaci na karni na 16 da'yan Hindu masu taurin kai suka yi a 1992, a cewar dogarawan da ke kula da ginin haikalin.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar Aug. 5 ga watan Fabarairun da ya gabata, inda masu shirya bikin suka ce taurari ne da ke cike da farin ciki ga'yan Hindu, amma kuma hakan ya nuna a shekara guda tun bayan da majalisar dokokin Indiya ta kwace matsayin kasa mai cin gashin kanta na yawancin al'ummar musulmi, Jammu da Kashmir.
Wannan alamari ba zai yiwu ba ga magoya baya da kuma masu adawa da jam'iyyar Modi mai ra'ayin rikau ta Bharatiya Janata Party, ko kuma BJP, wadanda a shekarun da suka gabata suka hada da alkawurra na kawar da cin gashin kan Kashmir da kuma gina haikali ga allahn Hindu Ram inda masallacin Mughal-era ya tsaya, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya da ke jihar Uttar Pradesh wanda masu ra'ayin rikau suka yi imanin cewa zai zama wurin haihuwa na Ram.
Saboda har yanzu cutar Koronabirus ta yadu a fadin kasar Indiya, wacce ta bayar da rahoton bullar cutar Koronabirus mafi girma a duniya, za a watsa bikin ne a gidan talabijin na jihar kuma za a takaita yawan mahalarta da'yan kallo, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kuma kungiyar Hindu ta duniya, wata kungiyar'yan kishin addinin Hindu da ke kawance da kungiyar ta BJP.
Haikalin zai zama "cibiyar samar da zaman lafiya mara mutuwa, hadin kan kasa da hadaka da kuma tada hankalin Hindutva", ko kuma hanyar rayuwar Hindu, in ji mai magana da yawun kungiyar Vinod Bansal a wata sanarwa da ya fitar a ranar Asabar.
