Ted Cruz ya ce manufofin Pelosi su ne "shoveling tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka"
Washington - Sanata Ted Cruz na Texas ya zargi kakakin majalisar wakilai Nancy Pelosi da'yan jam'iyyar Democrat da turawa wani kunshin agaji na coronavirus da mayar da hankali kan "shoveling cash a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka" a yayin da ake ci gaba da tattaunawa kan ma'auni na gaba.
A wata hira da ya yi da "Face the Nation" a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar na fuskantar tarzoma sau biyu a lokaci guda: Wata annoba ta duniya da ta yi ikirarin rayukan mutane sama da 600,000 a duniya da kuma "cikakken bala'in tattalin arziki" a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wanda ya bayyana a shafinsa na "Face the Nation" a gaban sanatan, "" bai mayar da hankali kan ko wadanne ba ".
"Manufarta ita ce shoveling tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka kasa", a cewar Texas Republican.
"Kuma musamman ma, ka duba takardar dala tiriliyan 3 da ta ke kokarin aikawa, kudi ne kawai ga abokanta kuma ba a magance matsalar ba. Manufarmu ita ce Amurkawa su na so su dawo bakin aiki. Su na so su iya samar wa iyalinsu ayyukan yi".
'Yan Majalisar Dattawa Republicans da kuma fadar White House sun shafe mako guda suna tattaunawa kan sharuddan karin wa'adin kashi na hudu na martanin da coronavirus ta bayar, wadanda suke sa ran za su kashe dala tiriliyan 1.
A karshen mako, shugaban ma'aikata na fadar White House Mark Meadows da kuma Sakataren Baitul mali Steven Mnuchin sun koma Capitol Hill domin karin tattaunawa da ma'aikatan majalisar, kuma Mnuchin ya fadawa gidan talbijin na Fox News a wata hira da suka yi a ranar Lahadi an bayyana cikakken bayanin da Shugaban Majalisar Dattijai Mitch McConnell ya yi a ranar Litinin.
Batun da ya fi ci wa'yan majalisar tuwo a kwarya - kuma wani batu na takaddama tsakanin'yan jam'iyyar Republican da kuma'yan Democrats - shi ne karewa da inganta amfanin marasa aikin yi, wanda ya fara tafiya a wannan karshen mako.
Yayin da'yan jam'iyyar Democrats ke son "kashi hudu" na kunshin coronavirus don ci gaba da bunkasa dala 600 ga amfanin,'yan jam'iyyar Republican suna kira da a gurfanar da su a gaban kuliya kuma suna jayayya da cewa wasu Amurkawa sun fi samun aikin yi fiye da yadda suka yi a albashi.
Cruz ya ce sama da rabin Amurkawa ne ke samun ingantaccen amfanin marasa aikin yi da ake biya a yanzu fiye da lokacin da suke aiki, ya kuma ce ya yi magana da kananan masu sana'o'i a Texas wadanda ke samun matsala ga ma'aikatan haya.
"Tabbas ba za su dawo ba saboda gwamnatin tarayya na biyan su, a wasu lokutta, sau biyu a matsayin kudi da za su zauna a gida", in ji shi.
